<div class="row" id="header">
  <div class="four columns centered">
    <img class="logo" src="/assets/home/logo.png"/>
  </div>
</div>
<div class="row main">
  <div class="columns seven">
    <div class="nine columns banner banner-left">
      <h3>Now with 100% less software!</h3>
    </div>
    <div class="twelve columns" id="about">
      <h4 class="brand1">Well, not really.</h4>
      <p>
        You may remember us as Gaslight Software, the premier
        Ruby on Rails shop in Cincinnati. We're not doing less software development
        these days, but we are doing more than software as well.
      </p>
      <p>
        We've been refining
        our Agile process, we've added designers to our team, and we've been working
        on platforms other than the web. Rather than let 'Software' limit what we do
        we've decided to let Gaslight stand alone as the source of innovation for your next project.
      </p>
      <h4 class="brand2">What We Do:</h4>
      <ul class="skills">
        <li><span>Ruby/Ruby on Rails</span></li>
        <li><span>Backbone JS</span></li>
        <li><span>iOS</span></li>
        <li><span>Embedded Systems</span></li>
      </ul>
      <ul class="skills">
        <li><span>Agile Process</span></li>
        <li><span>Design</span></li>
        <li><span>User Experience</span></li>
        <li><span><a href="http://training.gaslightsoftware.com">Training</a></span></li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="columns four offset-by-one">
    <div class="five columns banner banner-right offset-by-seven">
      <h3>Want to Talk?</h3>
    </div>

    <div class="twelve columns" id="contact">
      <%= render partial: 'contact/form' %>
      <div class="socialMedia">
        <ul class="icons">
          <li>
            <%= link_to("", "https://github.com/gaslight", class: "github") %>
          </li>
          <li>
            <%= link_to("", "https://facebook.com/teamgaslight", class: "facebook") %>
          </li>
          <li>
            <%= link_to("", "https://twitter.com/teamgaslight", class: "twitter") %>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>